{"tid":2173438,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"兵賊難分 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-25T08:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T08:02:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39f19e4fd6a3b1ea3a901f24adedf85a769127e6","tid":2173438,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/V3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2FV3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXUad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=e7976575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2FV3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54%2F&h=44992e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/V3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n兵賊難分 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3T60O4theAGeopTNsWdLb5T2OiU=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FLKGHSEJUBF45NP6FLFEHTKGXU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3T60O4theAGeopTNsWdLb5T2OiU%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFLKGHSEJUBF45NP6FLFEHTKGXU.JPG&h=52edeead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個16歲少年在旺角行街，被兩男一女三個自稱警務人員的成年人截停，要求檢查他們的財物，其間三男女盜走兩人各一部約值港幣10000元的手機，在襲擊其中一名少年後迅速逃逸。少年追截不果，去警局報案。案件列作冒充警務人員、盜竊及普通襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n這種奇案，在昔日香港，絕對不可能發生。因為根據《警察通例》第20-14（2）條，便衣人員「不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時」，一概必須表明身份及出示委任證。街頭截查巿民，便衣警必須主動出示委任證。若無委任證，巿民當然應該拒絕被查。<br />\n<br />\n但是，兩個少年敢拒絕嗎？不敢。7月24日晚，香港警察在其fb專頁發放一段影片，引用《警察通例》，辯稱警員並非必須在行動期間展示委任證。在這種刻意誤導之下，香港人敢質疑警員身份，敢不配合嗎？<br />\n<br />\n事實是，根據《警察通例》第20-14條第4段，當巿民要求警察出示委任證時，軍裝警員（而非便裝）必須立即出示委任證，除非（a）情況不容許﹔或（b）出示委任證會影響警隊行動及/或危及有關人員安全﹔或（c）要求不合理。所以警察在fb專頁發放的片段，刻意掩飾反送中運動以來警察的違例行為，為他們拒絕出示委任證的荒謬行為狡辯。並且，把亞洲最安全的城巿香港，變成兵賊難分的第三世界。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"29abbc7c6fd5ab7357235274458d620b2612df81","tid":2173438,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"女社工涉阻差 督察：騷證要求不合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2173436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2173436</a>"},{"pid":"fc03e0b3069f021a4f64bafab80a88d71423c02a","tid":2173438,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42f4eee195ef4b4cfcdad1f194d20910ed40a893","tid":2173438,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"兩男賊彩德邨冒警截查少年 盜走現金逃遁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2178912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2178912</a>"},{"pid":"63196e02b497b1c9f7b127849fc907d2313147ca","tid":2173438,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強私自改警例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419fa0daeeb1127e9a6d19b91ef08806f196bd41","tid":2173438,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"質疑進廈目的 要求抄低編號  女保安嚇退兩偽警<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192312</a>"},{"pid":"b2e3b55e55858dfea13772e2a25454c884f55000","tid":2173438,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"應該係休班狗嚟"}]}